{"tid":1327282,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"2019年離島區議會選舉討論","createTime":"2019-07-17T14:07:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-17T14:07:21.000Z","uid":281020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"7d4e4340fd79fdb1ccac090a3f551ec66759cd94","tid":1327282,"uid":281020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T14:07:21.000Z","msg":"離島區議會是香港十八個區議會之一，負責就新界離島區的事務向政府提供意見。是香港18個區議會中面積最大的地區。此區議會由10名民選議員及8名當然議員組成，最新一次的離島區議會選舉在2015年11月22日舉行。<br />\n<br />\n即係我哋要拎9席先可以打和super，全取10席先可以過半。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2TPVd19.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2TPVd19.png&h=7c1c149e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1ZYyCwTT7Yyx5wDpiB8eZVadha1e4f_Tsb_jddT42YPQ/edit?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheets%2Fd%2F1ZYyCwTT7Yyx5wDpiB8eZVadha1e4f_Tsb_jddT42YPQ%2Fedit%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=yxFCeCsiIqqjoL8q9QcQssTiFwqRwBg1VWT7Je45URE%3D&h=15a6889d\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1ZYyCwTT7Yyx5wDpiB8eZVadha1e4f_Tsb_jddT42YPQ/edit?usp=sharing</a> <br />\n今屆睇下可唔可以拉周浩鼎落馬、其他離島可唔可以有0的突破，例如大嶼山、二合一既長洲。<br />\n有冇坪洲、南丫島既巴絲打下民建聯，唔好比佢哋自動當選。<br />\n牙bill走咗去新界東選，好想挽留牙bill。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dllm.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}